# Project Setup Guide

## Environment Configuration
The project uses Docker for development. Key files:
- [docker-compose.yml](mdc:docker-compose.yml) for service configuration
- [Makefile](mdc:Makefile) for common commands

## Database Configuration
PostgreSQL database settings:
- Host: db
- Username: postgres
- Password: postgres
- Database: aceup_db

## Development Commands
Use make commands for common tasks:
```bash
make build    # Build all services
make start    # Start the services
make stop     # Stop all services
make db.init  # First-time database setup
make rails.c  # Access Rails console
make sh       # Access bash console
```

## Access Points
- Frontend: http://localhost:5173
- Backend API: http://localhost:3000

## Technical Stack
### Frontend
- React 19
- Vite
- TypeScript

### Backend
- Ruby on Rails 7.2 (API-only)
- Ruby 3.2
- PostgreSQL
